  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Acute first-ever stroke

          -  Left hemispheric stroke

          -  Korean version of Frenchay Aphasia Screening Test(K-FAST) &lt; 25 (less than 65 years
             old), K-FAST &lt;20 (65 years old and more than 65 years old) at 7 days after stroke
             onset

          -  Right handedness

        Exclusion Criteria:

